title: Mannie fresh interview and more

description:
Today on the show we had Mannie Fresh on the line where he spoke about his battle with Scott Storch, working with Lil Wayne and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man that punched his own mother over toilet paper, and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
